    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>wcmapper.rb</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>#!/usr/bin/ruby  -w
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>while line = gets
</span><span class='line'>  words = line.split(" ")
</span><span class='line'>  words.each{ |word| puts word.strip+"\t1"}
</span><span class='line'>end
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>wcreducer.rb</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
<span class='line-number'>16</span>
<span class='line-number'>17</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>#!/usr/bin/ruby  -w
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>current = nil
</span><span class='line'>count = 0
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>while line = gets
</span><span class='line'>  word, counter = line.split("\t")
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>  if word == current
</span><span class='line'>      count = count+1
</span><span class='line'>  else
</span><span class='line'>      puts current+"\t"+count.to_s if current
</span><span class='line'>      current = word
</span><span class='line'>      count = 1
</span><span class='line'>  end
</span><span class='line'>end
</span><span class='line'>puts current+"\t"+count.to_s</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Implementing WordCount using hadoop streaming</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
